  "description": "The key feature of this refrigerator is a stylish and attractive retro design, thanks to which the model can become a centerpiece in your kitchen decor. At the same time, the Gunter & Hauer FN 240 G refrigerator is presented on the market in three colours - classic white, red and black. The model is two-chamber with separate access doors to the freezer and refrigeration compartments. The total useful volume of the device is at the level of 212 liters. A small 46L freezer is placed on top with a minimum temperature maintained in the freezer of -32°C. The refrigerator compartment itself with a capacity of 166 liters is divided into four shelves, a compartment for vegetables and fruits, as well as several door shelves. The height of the model is only 147.5 cm. The noise generated during operation of the device does not exceed a relatively small 39 dB. It is also worth paying attention to the economical consumption of electricity - it corresponds to class A ++.",
